---

<footer class="bg-black border-t border-white/5 pt-24 pb-12 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute -bottom-40 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-6xl h-96 red-glow-strong opacity-20 pointer-events-none rounded-full"></div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-16 mb-24">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="size-9 bg-primary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">deployed_code</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter text-white uppercase">JÁUKEN</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
          Agencia digital especializada en diseño, estrategia y marketing de alto nivel. Elevamos el estándar digital de tu negocio.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-8 opacity-60">Navegación</h4>
        <nav class="flex flex-col gap-5">
          <a class="text-slate-400 hover:text-primary text-sm transition-colors w-fit" href="/">Inicio</a>
          <a class="text-slate-400 hover:text-primary text-sm transition-colors w-fit" href="/portafolio">Portafolio</a>
          <a class="text-slate-400 hover:text-primary text-sm transition-colors w-fit" href="/servicios">Servicios</a>
          <a class="text-slate-400 hover:text-primary text-sm transition-colors w-fit" href="/contacto">Contacto</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-8 opacity-60">Legal</h4>
        <nav class="flex flex-col gap-5">
          <a class="text-slate-400 hover:text-primary text-sm transition-colors w-fit" href="#">Privacidad</a>
          <a class="text-slate-400 hover:text-primary text-sm transition-colors w-fit" href="#">Términos</a>
          <a class="text-slate-400 hover:text-primary text-sm transition-colors w-fit" href="#">Cookies</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-8 opacity-60">Contacto</h4>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <a class="text-slate-300 hover:text-primary text-sm block font-medium transition-colors" href="mailto:contacto@jauken.agency">contacto@jauken.agency</a>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
            <a aria-label="Instagram" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1" href="#">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Instagram</span>
            </a>
            <a aria-label="LinkedIn" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1" href="#">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">LinkedIn</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-10 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-[10px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.1em]">
        © 2024 JÁUKEN DISEÑO DIGITAL. TODOS LOS DERECHOS RESERVADOS.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <div class="size-1 rounded-full bg-primary animate-pulse"></div>
        <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-medium">Crafted for Excellence</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>